{"id":6,"name":"EV006","note":"","pages":[{"conditions":{"actorId":1,"actorValid":false,"itemId":1,"itemValid":false,"selfSwitchCh":"A","selfSwitchValid":false,"switch1Id":1,"switch1Valid":false,"switch2Id":1,"switch2Valid":false,"variableId":1,"variableValid":false,"variableValue":0},"directionFix":false,"image":{"characterIndex":0,"characterName":"","direction":2,"pattern":0,"tileId":0},"list":[{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[115]},{"code":122,"indent":0,"parameters":[398,398,0,2,0,1]},{"code":111,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,398,0,0,0]},{"code":211,"indent":1,"parameters":[1]},{"code":357,"indent":1,"parameters":["TitleCg","openLock","解锁指定Cg",{"id":"66"}]},{"code":657,"indent":1,"parameters":["CgId = 66"]},{"code":241,"indent":1,"parameters":[{"name":"DHCM1_BGM02_Opening1","volume":90,"pitch":100,"pan":0}]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]遭擒后，阿欢就被人剥光了衣裳，以一种极为羞耻的姿势，束缚住了手脚。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]老鸨：多俊俏的姑娘家，何苦来哉，同享这世间乐事有何不可呢？"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]徐娘半老的老鸨满头珠钗，兰花指捏着丝绢扫过阿欢的脸庞，半是真情，半怀假意。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]她是见多识广了的，也微微佩服这小小丫头的重情重义，却也觉得小小丫头撑不了多久，现在不过是在逞着强，自找那苦头，略施手段就能被降服了的。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]多烈性的女子，她都降服过，何况这一眼就知不通人事的丫头。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]于是乎，只是来看了两眼,就唤上人，她先去歇歇，喝喝茶，静待半柱香的时间，包这丫头已经是春江水暖。"]},{"code":222,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"29-3-TJ1",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]羞愤熏得脸蛋通红，红到耳尖，阿欢咬着贝齿不肯出声，是她不够小心，原是想为小姐分忧解难，却似要拖累小姐了。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]乳峰被绳索勒得更加突出，手也被捆在身后，动惮不得，最难以言齿的是双腿处——小腿被折在大腿根。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]又往两边打开，明明是极度隐秘之处，此处却显于众人眼前。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]老鸨刚出得门，久候的男子就迎了上来。阿欢感受到他的接近，想躲却无处可躲。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]越是挣扎，绳索竟捆得愈紧，粗糙的麻绳勒娇嫩的肌肤生疼，不消片刻就已然见到与麻绳相交处的雪肤一片片繁星似的红点，端得是又疼又痒，好似有蚂蚁在咬。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]男人见此情形却似如获至宝。他取出一根黑色皮鞭，手把握在掌心，轻轻一甩就是一声响脆的破空之音。"]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"29-3-TJ2",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]阿欢心头一颤，却亦不开口，直至细长条的鞭子甩到她的身上，冷不丁吓到了她，一声惊呼后紧忙又咬住了唇。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]被抽打到的地方，初始并不见疼。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]然而，很快巨疼的感觉闪似传来，就这一瞬的痛感之后缓缓接着绵绵的痒意，火辣辣的痒。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]刚想去努力克服这难受的感觉，下一鞭又落了下来，又是先痛后痒的感觉，一颗颗汗水从光滑的额头与鼻尖渗出，滚落下来。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]男人却是美滋滋看着眼前美景，凝脂上先浮出一道惨白鞭痕，一须臾就浮肿变红，似冬日腊梅。在一声声破空之音中，一枝枝盛放开来。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]男人伸出手，去抚摸自己的佳作。本就火辣辣的伤在触碰下更是痛得阿欢周身颤抖。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]兴致勃然的男人反手握着鞭子，用着手把拨弄阿欢可怜的，怯怯翕动的蜜穴。穴口处是湿漉漉的一片，粘着蜜汁，手把一点点被转动着插进去。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]泪水聚在眼眶，打着转不肯落下。男人抽出手把，掏出自己的阳具抵在阿欢的穴口，大手蹂躏起被冷落甚久的雪乳。"]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"29-3-TJ3",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":230,"indent":1,"parameters":[60]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"29-3-TJ4",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":230,"indent":1,"parameters":[40]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"29-3-TJ5",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]在阿欢刚僵硬的身体微微放松时，猛然插入。"]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"29-3-TJ6",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]痛！一大颗泪水滚落下来，小声的呜咽从唇间溢出。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]沉思片刻，男人拿出一瓶膏药，涂了少许到阿欢的蜜豆与穴内。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]先是清凉的感觉，然而渐渐变成热烫，酥痒，渴望着被狠狠欺负了去。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]男人涂完药就肆意玩弄了会儿蜜豆，就着新溢出的蜜汁，阳具又插入穴内。这次显然比头一遭受到了更服帖的热情款待。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]此时，他反而不急，用起九浅一深的套路，逼得阿欢悄悄提臀相迎。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]男人直接点破，拍打起阿欢伤痕累累的雪臀，肉浪滚滚煞是好看。"]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"29-3-TJ7",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]明明应该痛得不行，但是从这痛中，莫名得到了一阵阵爽利的快感。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]不想挨了打，不想受疼，却又想被再多打几巴掌，解解痒…"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]阿欢的心跳加速，矛盾的想法撕裂着意识。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]男人突然发起狂风骤雨般的进攻，冲碎了阿欢已然不坚定的意志，穴内开始一阵一阵紧缩，是快到了的样子，男人突然抽出，把阿欢干晾起。"]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"29-3-TJ5",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]恶劣地低头在她耳边轻语。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]龟公：小娘子还要是不要？"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]阿欢还想抵抗，男人的手捏住蜜豆，轻轻揉捏，穴内更是可怜吐着清液，想要，就差一点就到了顶端。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]阿欢再也抵挡不住。带着哭腔，请求男人的插入。"]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"29-3-TJ7",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":230,"indent":1,"parameters":[50]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"29-3-TJ8",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":230,"indent":1,"parameters":[40]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"29-3-TJ9",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":230,"indent":1,"parameters":[30]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"29-3-TJ10",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":230,"indent":1,"parameters":[30]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,"29-3-TJ12",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]等老鸨再回来之时，阿欢已经变成个小荡妇，快乐地享受起来了。"]},{"code":122,"indent":1,"parameters":[143,143,0,0,1]},{"code":121,"indent":1,"parameters":[342,342,0]},{"code":201,"indent":1,"parameters":[0,82,10,33,2,0]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[1]},{"code":211,"indent":1,"parameters":[1]},{"code":117,"indent":1,"parameters":[116]},{"code":0,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":412,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":111,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,398,0,1,0]},{"code":211,"indent":1,"parameters":[1]},{"code":357,"indent":1,"parameters":["TitleCg","openLock","解锁指定Cg",{"id":"67"}]},{"code":657,"indent":1,"parameters":["CgId = 67"]},{"code":241,"indent":1,"parameters":[{"name":"DHCM1_BGM02_Opening1","volume":90,"pitch":100,"pan":0}]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]阿欢被众人带到了房间，自从进来，她就明白自己会面对的遭遇。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]可真到的时候，被人们脱下衣服，仅剩柔滑的丝带缠绕着赤裸的自己时，阿欢还是有一丝慌乱。"]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]阿欢：不要...求求你们... ..."]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\\CT[1]可是没有人在乎她的感受，都到妓院来了，一切挣扎只是徒劳。"]},{"code":222,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":231,"indent":1,"parameters